# 📝 To-Do List App (Node.js + MVC)

✨ A simple and dynamic To-Do List application built using **Node.js**, **Express**, and **EJS** following the **MVC architecture**.

---

## 📖 Overview

This project allows users to manage daily tasks efficiently.
You can add, delete, and mark tasks as completed.

It is designed for beginners to understand:

* Backend development with Node.js
* MVC structure
* Dynamic rendering with EJS

---

## 🚀 Features

* ✅ Add new tasks
* ✅ View all tasks
* ✅ Delete tasks
* ✅ Mark tasks as completed
* ✅ Clean and responsive UI
* ✅ MVC folder structure

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* ⚙️ Node.js
* 🚀 Express.js
* 🧩 EJS Template Engine
* 🎨 HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* 🗄️ MongoDB (optional)

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```id="6rmb82"
todo-app/
│
├── models/           # Task schema
├── views/            # EJS templates
│   ├── index.ejs
│
├── controllers/      # Business logic
├── routes/           # App routes
├── public/           # Static files (CSS, JS)
│
├── app.js            # Main server file
├── package.json
└── README.md
```

---

## ⚡ Installation

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash id="b48o3g"
git clone https://github.com/your-username/todo-app.git
cd todo-app
```

---

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies

```bash id="qhtlw0"
npm install
```

---

### 3️⃣ Run the App

```bash id="jg7s7j"
node app.js
```

or (for development)

```bash id="cdpn70"
nodemon app.js
```

---

## 🌐 Usage

* Open browser
* Visit:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

* Add tasks
* Mark them complete
* Delete when done

---

## 🧠 How It Works

### 🔹 Model

Stores task data (title, description, status)

### 🔹 View

EJS templates display tasks dynamically

### 🔹 Controller

Handles logic (add, delete, update tasks)

